    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>LONGER VIEW OF QUALITY</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>List of Consumer Reports' predicted reliability ratings for three most recent model years; photos; chart (M)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Initial Quality Study by J. D. Power &amp; Associates measures problems that arise in the first 90 days of ownership. Many consumers find longer-term studies more useful; one assessment is Consumer Reports' predicted reliability ratings, based on surveys of readers for the three most recent model years (or two in cases of recently redesigned vehicles).</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
